{"tid":2077662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我愛中國 所以我唔用国貨","createTime":"2020-06-24T12:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T14:06:52.000Z","uid":356849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6f6b9c8bd918b01b8785678da4dfc0688a159c64","tid":2077662,"uid":356849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:31:40.000Z","msg":"相信大家都聽過唔少有關中國使用童工嘅事件，就好似以下呢個case咁<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.scmp.com/news/china/society/article/2048231/clothing-factories-eastern-china-import-child-labour-migrant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fsociety%2Farticle%2F2048231%2Fclothing-factories-eastern-china-import-child-labour-migrant&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=5e2f457b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.scmp.com/news/china/society/article/2048231/clothing-factories-eastern-china-import-child-labour-migrant</a><br />\n<br />\n次次一諗起啲小朋友比人當奴隸咁用，我個心真係好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再諗起原來中国咁多廉價商品都係由童工所做嘅，我想講我真係再買唔落去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係唔想我国嘅GDP係透過榨壓非法童工先可以去到咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見及此，為左改變我国非法童工嘅情況，我決定唔會再買国貨住，從而話比啲工廠知佢哋咁做係唔啱嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多位如果係有基本良心嘅 都應該跟我一樣放棄用国貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就當係為咗我国小朋友嘅未來著想啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntldr: 罷買国貨 改善我国小童未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403502a2a9b7bff074f9ae22b2a788f127488787","tid":2077662,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:32:19.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"03b8b6138afc4678e56ac8b08bde1a19607dbab6","tid":2077662,"uid":356849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:47:21.000Z","msg":"推下 等多啲有心人可以睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a381f5c5a207c5816f931c307fe9e2a381a0db2e","tid":2077662,"uid":356849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:55:19.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"cbbb31bd797bd80f4fb16357093b39e18d08070f","tid":2077662,"uid":356849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:55:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c15f58779ebc331843af7674e0a05051f88bbbfb","tid":2077662,"uid":356849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}